## Triage report

While I think the keyboard hiding and loss of focus is consistent with the native iOS behavior, `onFieldSubmitted` being called I would consider a bug.  I can also reproduce this on Chrome on iOS.

Upon further testing, I see that is only occurs with a `prefixIcon` or `suffixIcon` in the an `InputDecoration` on the `TextFormField`.

